name: MLImageSizeConstraintType
desc: The modes that determine how the model defines a feature's image size constraint.

items.name: case range
items.desc: The image feature accepts image sizes defined by a range of widths and a range of heights.

items.name: case enumerated
items.desc: The image feature accepts image sizes listed in an array.

items.name: case unspecified
items.desc: The image size constraint is not configured and should be ignored.
